        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">A couple of weeks back (at lvl 52) I went to camp for one. Not too bad getting there (had top summon 49 pet) but holding the area isn't a no brainer like the frenzy camp etc. There are lots of spawns, some of which HT, some are cleric mobs and some are wizards. All this mean't I had to heal my pet a heck of a lot and I nearly died at one point when I got HT'd after pacting pet (went down to 80hp heh). After 4 hours I hadn't even had a bodyguard spawn so I gave up and bought one for 1.5k the next day. Best money I've ever spent as it's a god send in SoV, I've explored a load of places solo that I wouldn't even dream of doing if I had to rely on casting invis.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
