        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Side note tactic I discovered while doing Phenocryst Focus Quest.</P><P>Agro'ed MOB on me I got off a successful FD.  Goo's in Phenocryst caves don't leave you and wander off.  Using hot keys, mouse clicking too slow, I stood up (Stand key #5) and then VERY quickly used my Circlet (Key #7) and they did not agro.</P><P>Ran out of the cave and clicked off invis and Goo's came.  Repeated same result. </P><P>Whoohooo, this is a wonderful thing!</P><P>-Kuotat</P><P><BR> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
